          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much do AI sales agents cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Prices range from free (Apollo.io, Clay free tiers) to $10,000+/month for enterprise autonomous platforms. Most mid-market B2B teams spend $500–$2,500/month — compared to $5,000–$8,000/month for one human SDR's salary and benefits.</div>
