          <div class="faq-answer">For top-of-funnel prospecting and meeting booking, yes — AI agents now match or exceed human SDR output at a fraction of the cost. For complex enterprise deals requiring deep relationship building over months, human SDRs still outperform. Best teams use AI for volume and humans for relationships.</div>
